{"type":"answer","id":9755,"parentType":"question","parentId":2198,"uid":1655,"contents":"吼啊，我当然是滋滋的。<br>\n<br>\n不只让党中央能深切地明白<b>十三亿人的根本需要</b>，让能加强对言论的控制，让中央和人民群众<b>打成一片</b>(字面意思，指肢体上的强烈交流)。<br>\n<br>\n这也可以让中央更准确的<b>实弹抓捕</b>某些螳臂挡车的歹徒，让军方解决了<b>子弹泛滥</b>的根本问题，增加子弹使用量，推动<b>GDP(迫真)</b>发展，更能实现<b>中国特色社会主义</b>，国富則民强。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533701585635724.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533701585635724.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533701585635724.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533701618493016.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533701618493016.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533701618493016.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-08-08","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}